title: Jonny Lieberman & Jethro Bovgindon
description:
Jonny and Jethro are the hosts of Motor Trend's "Head 2 Head", where they drive and compare all of the fastest and coolest cars around. 

****DISCLAIMER: When we recorded this show, our WireCast software took a digital dump. This audio comes from a backup recording that was recorded on an iPhone, and started 15 minutes in. We apologize for the audio quality. The issue has since been fixed. ****

 

This show is a video: https://youtu.be/brl3cTzHq6A

IG: @thesmokingtire @fakezackklapman @jonnylieberman @jethrobovindon
